description:
Senator Rick Scott joins Buck to discuss the Democrats failed effort to end the filibuster, as well as Biden's epic failures on the economy and border. Buck's take on shameless Senate Dems failing to end the filibuster. Buck answers calls on Ukraine and the Democrats' Jim Crow 2.0 lie. OutKick breaks another big story on the Penn trans swimmer. Matt Walsh tells Dr. Phil the truth about the trans agenda.
